meanings: Pronoun, Determiner (의문문에서) 무엇, 몇, 어떤, 무슨 (→which)
Pronoun, Determiner (…한) 것[일], 어떤[무슨] 것[일], …하는 모든
뭐라고?(남의 말을 못 들었거나 이해가 안 될 때)
왜[뭐]?(남의 말을 듣고 뭘 원하는지 물을 때)
Pronoun 무엇, 어떤 것[일], 무슨 일[물건], 얼마, 얼마 정도
Adjective (…하는) 그[저], (…하는) 그것[저것]들의, (…하는) 만큼의, (…하는) 어떠한, 여하한(that[those]...which)

1.)W-Hat is a group in Second Life for members of the Something Awful Forums. 2.)W-hat or :w-hat: came shortly after the "what" craze in FYAD/GBS. The image was at first a clever way of saying "what" and later a way of saying "what" without a ban... for a while.
